Project Proposal: Chennai Flood 2015 Relief Android App

Project Overview:
The purpose of this project is to develop an Android application that provides easy access to all emergency contacts related to Chennai flood relief. The app will be published in the Google Play Store, and the development process will be completed in a day.

Project Objectives:
To develop an Android app that provides easy access to all emergency contacts related to Chennai flood relief.
To provide a user-friendly interface that allows users to quickly and easily find the information they need.
To publish the app in the Google Play Store, ensuring that it is accessible to as many people as possible.
To complete the project within a day, ensuring that it is available for use during the ongoing flood relief efforts.

Project Scope:
The scope of the project includes the development of an Android application that provides access to all emergency contacts related to Chennai flood relief. The app will have a simple user interface, allowing users to quickly find the information they need. The app will include the following features:
List of emergency contacts related to Chennai flood relief, including phone numbers.
Option to save frequently used emergency contacts as favorites for quick access.
Option to share emergency contact information with others via email, text message, or social media.

Project Plan:
Project planning and research. This includes identifying the most important emergency contacts and gathering information about the ongoing flood relief efforts.
App design and development. This includes creating the user interface, integrating the emergency contact information, and implementing the interactive map.
Testing and debugging. This includes ensuring that the app is functioning properly and fixing any bugs that are found.
App deployment and publication. This includes submitting the app to the Google Play Store and ensuring that it is available for download.

Project Deliverables:
A fully functional Android application that provides access to all emergency contacts related to Chennai flood relief.
Option to share emergency contact information with others via email, text message, or social media.

Conclusion:
The Chennai Flood Relief Android app will be a valuable resource for people affected by the ongoing flood crisis. By providing easy access to emergency contacts and important information, the app will help people find the help they need quickly and easily. With a development timeline of just a day, we aim to deliver a high-quality app that will be available for use during the ongoing relief efforts.




